    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase the ISA limit - \u00a320k for cash ISA's and \u00a320k for stocks & shares ISA's",
        "additional_details": "There have been reports the Government is considering reducing ISA's. We think splitting the ISA into two, \u00a320k for cash ISA's and \u00a320k for stocks and shares ISA's could protect and reassure early savers that their money is safe in the banking system. We think it would give residents the chance to save and invest each year.",
        "background": "We think increasing the ISA limit to \u00a340k and splitting it into two will give UK residents the chance to save and invest. We think this would support both saving and investing in the UK",
